org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl

Class OgmQueryTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl.LegacyParserBridgeQueryTranslator
      • org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl.OgmQueryTranslator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryTranslator

    public class OgmQueryTranslator
extends LegacyParserBridgeQueryTranslator
    A QueryTranslator which converts JP-QL queries into store-dependent native queries, e.g. Cypher queries for Neo4j or DBObject-based queries for MongoDB.

    Query conversion is done by invoking the dialect's query parser service. Results are loaded through OgmQueryLoader. Depending on whether a store supports parameterized queries (Neo4j does, MongoDB doesn't) we either use one and the same loader for a query executed several times with different parameter values or we create a new loader for each set of parameter values.

    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
